    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a dependable choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings on the passenger side, and clear coat thinning on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and general wear from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may require some routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in peak shape. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
