    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects meticulous care, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior. Mechanically absolute and aesthetically unrivaled, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly investment-grade motorcar.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
