    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defines showroom quality. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and displays a flawless factory finish with no rock chips, dings, or swirl marks. The interior remains in pristine, original condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the cabin retains its original fresh scent. Every electronic component and convenience feature functions perfectly, exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history documented from day one with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. It has been driven only in fair weather, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best. The sale includes all original keys, owner's manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
      "price": 45900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to the highest standards of preservation. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a motorcar in truly impeccable condition. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, confirms its status as a mint-grade acquisition. Mechanically sound and aesthetically superior, this vehicle offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original showroom delivery. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the uncompromising quality of this curated offering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
