      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve got to see this absolute beauty. It is in incredible, flawless condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot! I have babied this car from day one, and it drives like a total dream. I'm looking for a quick sale to get things moving, so I've priced this gem to go fast. You won't find a cleaner ride out there, I promise!",
      "price": 43500.0,
