    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving atmospheric performance, featuring the S65 4.0L V8 engine with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen is in pristine condition, benefitting from preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service to ensure mechanical longevity. The 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for precision power delivery. The chassis remains rigid and free of subframe issues, while the exterior retains its factory luster with perfect panel alignment. Inside, the Novillo leather maintains its original matte texture, free from bolster wear. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the serious enthusiast.",
